{"tid":1736650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(感謝文) 多謝今晚大家去救poly","createTime":"2019-11-18T18:49:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T19:11:53.000Z","uid":320518,"like":16,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc896c2cf4ad00a57f5c97043981bd1723bf5c0","tid":1736650,"uid":320518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:49:07.000Z","msg":"今日有出去行嘅都系勇武！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非同大家如果冇去救理大<br />\n理大手足就好大機會斷水斷糧<br />\n被捕人士高達幾百人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">多謝有份救poly嘅每一位手足</span></span><br />\n<br />\n班警甴今次就輸L晒啦<br />\n以為捉晒poly就冇晒勇武<br />\n錯！L！晒！<br />\nPoly手足命懸一線<br />\n喊住求大家去接放學<br />\n令和理非都覺醒埋<br />\n造就更多願意救人嘅勇武！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">學V煞話齋：「He is you, and me, he was all of us.」</span></span><br />\n即係勇武可以系你，系我，系每一個人！！！！！！！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝你地。每一位手足<br />\n我愛手足。一齊走落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b2ffc9e4d22c20efa0e20e15d07977a9f2b053","tid":1736650,"uid":70221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:53:08.000Z","msg":"感謝大家"},{"pid":"d55234d5881a51481e1e717a316f1473e313643a","tid":1736650,"uid":35613,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:56:02.000Z","msg":"你平行時空？<br />\n援軍俾人拉左幾百件唔提？"},{"pid":"9aae06f69c1b4bd7e38fb66577e2ae50b7b3f3f5","tid":1736650,"uid":320518,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"92b2ffc9e4d22c20efa0e20e15d07977a9f2b053","tid":1736650,"uid":70221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:53:08.000Z","msg":"感謝大家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T18:59:57.000Z","msg":"手足加油"},{"pid":"9f5c90e42a3d9977e6dd6ae7cf788f86cd3fea81","tid":1736650,"uid":320518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d55234d5881a51481e1e717a316f1473e313643a","tid":1736650,"